### Observations
- Feature-based structure is mostly consistent across 5 modules
- Hono server setup is well-structured with CORS, logger, error handling, 404 handler
- API route handler exports GET/POST/PATCH/DELETE (compliant with API-01)
- [AppType](file:///d:/scientific-journals-website/src/server/app.ts#74-75) is correctly exported for RPC typing
- Prisma singleton uses lazy initialization (`ENV-02` compliant)
- Admin dashboard uses server-side rendering with direct Prisma calls (correct for RSC)
- Tests exist for schemas, serialization, pagination, API routes, and auth

