## ARCHITECTURE COMPLIANCE

### Violations by `rule_id`

| Rule | Description | Status | Details |
|---|---|---|---|
| **FEAT-SERVER-04** | UUID required for identifiers | ❌ VIOLATED | All 9 Prisma models use `BigInt @id @default(autoincrement())` |
| **UI-01** | Shared components only | ⚠️ PARTIAL | Google Translate widget is a custom non-standard component, not a shared UI primitive |
| **UI-02** | Visual consistency | ⚠️ PARTIAL | Translation button has inconsistent styling vs. rest of navbar |
| **FEAT-API-02** | React Query required | ⚠️ PARTIAL | OJS hook ([use-get-ojs-journals.ts](file:///d:/scientific-journals-website/src/features/ojs/api/use-get-ojs-journals.ts)), login page, verify-code page use raw `fetch` instead of RPC client |
| **FEAT-SERVER-02** | Zod validation required | ⚠️ PARTIAL | OJS route (`/ojs/journals`) has no Zod validation |
| **NAME-01** | Kebab-case naming | ✅ COMPLIANT | All files use kebab-case |
| **ARCH-01** | Feature-based structure | ✅ COMPLIANT | All features under `src/features/` |
| **ARCH-02** | Feature structure pattern | ⚠️ PARTIAL | OJS feature missing `schemas/` directory |
| **ENV-01** | Env vars documented | ✅ COMPLIANT | `.env.production.template` exists |
| **ENV-02** | Lazy initialization | ✅ COMPLIANT | Both Prisma and OJS pool use lazy init |
| **DEP-01** | No new deps without approval | ✅ COMPLIANT | No unauthorized packages detected |
| **API-01** | Only get/post/patch/delete | ✅ COMPLIANT | Only these methods exported |

### Critical Issues

1. **🔴 Homepage Numbers Hardcoded** — Stats `250+`, `15000+`, `50000+`, `120+` are static values in `app/page.tsx` lines 56–77, not connected to any database
2. **🔴 RPC Client Typed as `any`** — `src/lib/rpc.ts` line 9: `export const client: any = hc<AppType>(...)` — destroys end-to-end type safety
3. **🔴 Hardcoded Credentials in `init.ts`** — Email `ellarousi@gmail.com` with password `WMssg_k2` and `www.alshebani88@gmail.com` with password `00000000` hardcoded in database seed
4. **🔴 OTP Only Logs to Console** — `console.log()` in auth route.ts lines 47, 152 — no email delivery configured

### High Priority Issues

5. **🟠 BigInt IDs Instead of UUID** — Entire schema uses `BigInt @default(autoincrement())`, violating `FEAT-SERVER-04`. Requires migration.
6. **🟠 Fake Dashboard Stat** — `app/admin/dashboard/page.tsx` line 106: `Total Authors = submissions * 0.7` — purely fabricated number
7. **🟠 No Skeleton Loaders Used** — `Skeleton` component exists in `components/ui/skeleton.tsx` but is never used anywhere. `app/loading.tsx` returns `null`.
8. **🟠 Google Translate Hydration Issue** — External script injection in `useEffect` causes the translation widget to appear/disappear during hydration

