## FRONTEND ANALYSIS

### UI Consistency
- ✅ Radix UI primitives used consistently (15 in `components/ui/`)
- ✅ Shared `Card`, `Button`, `Input`, `Label` components used across pages
- ⚠️ Google Translate widget uses inline styles (`minHeight: "40px"`) instead of Tailwind
- ⚠️ Error/success messages in verify-code and login pages use inline Tailwind classes for alerts instead of a shared Alert component

### Shared Components Usage
- ✅ `Navbar`, `Footer`, `AdminSidebar`, `AdminHeader` properly componentized
- ✅ `GSAPWrapper`, `AnimatedCounter` provide animation consistently
- ⚠️ No shared `EmptyState` component — empty states are ad-hoc inline JSX

### React Query Compliance
- ✅ `useGetJournals`, `useCreateJournal`, `useGetJournal` use RPC client via `client.journals.$get()`
- ✅ `useLogin`, `useRegister`, `useLogout` use RPC client via `client.auth.*.$post()`
- ❌ `useGetOjsJournals` uses raw `fetch("/api/ojs/journals")` — bypasses RPC
- ❌ `app/admin/login/page.tsx` uses raw `fetch("/api/auth/login")` — bypasses RPC
- ❌ `app/admin/verify-code/page.tsx` uses raw `fetch("/api/auth/verify-code")` and `fetch("/api/auth/resend-code")` — bypasses RPC

### Skeleton Usage
- `Skeleton` component defined but **never imported or used anywhere**
- `app/loading.tsx` returns `null` — no loading UI for page transitions
- Only `Loader2` spinner icon used for loading (journals on homepage)
- Admin submissions page has its own `loading.tsx` (not yet inspected)

### Hardcoded Values
- ❌ `app/page.tsx` lines 56–77: `250+`, `15000+`, `50000+`, `120+` — fully static
- ❌ `app/admin/dashboard/page.tsx` line 106: `submissions * 0.7` as "Total Authors"
- ⚠️ OTP expiration is hardcoded to `5 * 60 * 1000` (5 minutes) — should be configurable

