## BACKEND ANALYSIS

### Hono Routing
- ✅ All routes registered via `app.route()` in `src/server/app.ts`
- ✅ Mounted routes: `/journals`, `/solutions`, `/auth`, `/messages`, `/ojs`
- ✅ Base path `/api` set correctly
