## AUTHENTICATION REVIEW

### Session Validation Logic
- ✅ **Middleware-level protection**: `middleware.ts` uses `jose.jwtVerify()` for all admin routes
- ✅ **Server-side protection**: `app/admin/dashboard/page.tsx` calls `getSession()` + `redirect()`
- ✅ Cookie-based JWT with `httpOnly`, `secure` (production), `sameSite: "lax"`
- ✅ 7-day token expiration
- ✅ Login page redirects to dashboard if token is valid
- ⚠️ No CSRF protection beyond sameSite cookie

### Dashboard Protection
- ✅ Middleware blocks all `/admin/*` routes without valid JWT
- ✅ Dashboard page has server-side session check with redirect
- ✅ Admin layout correctly excludes auth pages from sidebar/header
- ✅ `requireAdmin` middleware enforces `admin|superadmin` role on API routes

### OTP Verification System
- ✅ 6-digit numeric OTP generated via `Math.random()` ⚠️ (not cryptographically secure)
- ✅ 5-minute expiration enforced
- ✅ Previous codes invalidated before generating new one
- ✅ Code marked as `used: true` after verification
- ✅ Resend cooldown (60s) enforced on client
- ❌ **No email delivery** — OTP only logged to `console.log()`
- ❌ Rate limiting missing on `/resend-code` endpoint (server-side)
- ⚠️ Register endpoint bypasses OTP — creates session immediately

### Email Templates
- ❌ **No email templates exist** — no email service configured at all

### Token Lifecycle
- ✅ JWT issued with `setIssuedAt()` and `setExpirationTime("7d")`
- ✅ Cookie `maxAge` matches JWT expiration (7 days)
- ✅ Logout destroys cookie

---

