### Missing Env Variables
- ⚠️ `ALLOW_PROD_DB_INIT` — Not in template, required for `init.ts` to function
- ⚠️ `SESSION_EXPIRY` — Defined in `.env` but never used in code (JWT uses hardcoded `"7d"`)

### Lazy Initialization Issues
- ✅ Prisma client lazy-initialized via `createPrismaClient()` function
- ✅ OJS pool lazy-initialized via `getPool()` function
- ✅ Both use env var checks before connecting
- ⚠️ `init.ts` creates a separate PrismaClient instance for seeding — this is intentional but creates a second connection pool

